OL,3,CTrial to explore if special tampon
OL,4,Ccould help detect ovarian cancer early
OL,6,FA new trial will explore if a special
OL,7,Fmedical tampon can help detect the
OL,8,Fearliest signs of ovarian cancer.
OL,10,FThe test uses the medical tampon and
OL,11,Fswabs to looks for tiny biological
OL,12,Fsignals in vaginal fluid and could be
OL,13,Fa "complete gamechanger" for the
OL,14,Fdisease, which is usually diagnosed at
OL,15,Fan advanced stage.
OL,17,F250 women are being recruited for the
OL,18,Ftrial, known as Violet and led by
OL,19,Fresearchers in Southampton.
