OL,6,FIt will include patients who have been
OL,7,Fdiagnosed with ovarian cancer and are
OL,8,Fhaving their ovaries removed, as well
OL,9,Fas women with the BRCA gene mutation
OL,10,Fwho are choosing to have risk-reducing
OL,11,Fsurgery.
OL,13,FPeople with this gene mutation have a
OL,14,Fhigher risk of developing a number of
OL,15,Fcancers, such as breast and ovarian.
