OL,3,CTrial to explore if special tampon
OL,4,Ccould help detect ovarian cancer early
OL,6,FDr Jemma Longley, consultant medical
OL,7,Foncologist at University Hospital
OL,8,FSouthampton and chief investigator for
OL,9,Fthe trial, said: "There is currently
OL,10,Fno screening programme available for
OL,11,Fovarian cancer, and women with
OL,12,Frecognised genetic mutations, such as
OL,13,FBRCA, may opt to have surgery to
OL,14,Fremove their ovaries and fallopian
OL,15,Ftubes to reduce their risk of
OL,16,Fdeveloping the disease.
OL,18,F"However, this can have significant
OL,19,Flong-term health effects by putting
OL,20,Fyounger women into a surgical
OL,21,Fmenopause."
