OL,3,CTrial to explore if special tampon
OL,4,Ccould help detect ovarian cancer early
OL,6,FResearchers will also take tissue from
OL,7,Fthe removed ovaries and fallopian
OL,8,Ftubes and compare them to those
OL,9,Fwithout the disease.
OL,11,FThe samples will be analysed for the
OL,12,Fearliest signs of ovarian cancer, with
OL,13,Fexperts looking for changes in
OL,14,Fbiomarkers known as microRNAs, tiny
OL,15,Fbiological signals that are present in
OL,16,Fboth ovarian cancer cells and vaginal
OL,17,Ffluid.
OL,19,FThere are around 7,600 new cases of
OL,20,Fovarian cancer in the UK each year but
OL,21,Fmany are diagnosed at a late stage.
